AccurateTax,is,a,web,based,service,that,allows,users,to,manage,the,sales,tax,collection,and,remittance,for,their,e,commerce,websites,The,system,provides,sales,tax,rates,on,each,order,and,product,during,checkout,sales,tax,reports,and,address,validation,This,functionality,is,accessible,via,an,XML,based,API,that,can,be,used,to,integrate,with,third,party,applications,Interested,developers,should,contact,the,provider,for,more,information